Let \mathcal {A} be a reflexive graph. A displayed reflexive graph \mathcal {B}\equiv 
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen 
 \mathopen {}\left \lvert \mathcal {B}\right \rvert \mathclose {}
,\approx _{\mathcal {B}}^{\bullet },\mathsf {rx}_{\mathcal {B}}^{\bullet }\right \rparen \mathclose {}
